S. Thorne
5,0 z 5 gwiazdek EXCELLENT JACKET!
Opinia napisana w Kanadzie dnia 26 stycznia 2021
Rozmiar: XLKolor: ZielonyZweryfikowany zakup
This jacket is awesome! It takes the origional M65 and improves on it to make a Cold Weather lined jacket that keep me warm and comfortabke on the job site at -30 deg. C. I AM 6 feet tall and 115 lbs with a muscular build. A T-Shirt and a sweater fit perfect under this jacket. I have a little longer arms and the sleves fully cover them fully extended. If you are a little smaller it will be baggy for sure. I can be comfortable in just a T-Shirt as well by just tightening the draw strings. I love the mobility of this jacket! Its not really stiff like a Carhartt. Jacket is made in China, but Brandit does a "German" level of quality control! So no worries there. Only point of improvement would be to either update the picture of the "Olive" picture on the website as it looks much more worn in the picture, but it arrives looking fresh and green...but what ever, Im looking forward to breaking it in myself! If Brandit could provide a worn in model simular to the one picture, that would be Amazing! Other then that this is an exceptional item that I am looking forward years of use and priced very well!

Rozmiar: MKolor: CzarnyZweryfikowany zakup
My teen son is on the autism spectrum and is very sensory and particular. My brother had this jacket so my son tried it on and loved it. He showed us where to order it on Amazon and said it may take awhile to get here from the UK. It came in a very short time period, less than expected, and its all my son wears. Size is true and quality is great! Highly recommend this jacket.
